{"tid":96232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方食環達成共識，若有無牌小販，即出防暴清場","createTime":"2017-01-26T16:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T09:54:44.000Z","uid":58099,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df80687ed40de64b26ff577ff8b466889489c6b6","tid":96232,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"為防去年初一旺角騷亂再臨，警方將最少出動1,500全副武裝防暴警於年三十晚至初四期間，在旺角及深水埗等多個小販擺賣黑點巡邏，警方亦會加派便衣警搜集情報。消息指西九龍總區指揮官卓孝業會親自督師，若再爆嚴重衝突，料警隊決不手軟。 <br />\n<br />\n防暴隊屆時會全副武裝，包括盾牌、大支裝胡椒噴劑、胡椒球、催淚煙彈、橡膠子彈等。據悉警方與食環署達成共識，若有無牌小販，食環人員將立即聯絡警方出動防暴清場，不會與他們周旋。"},{"pid":"9e3d1a035bf08671e6e0b92214c6f34a2ef3da8d","tid":96232,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"到時十幾個豬嘴盾牌佬圍住一個魚蛋阿伯就好笑"},{"pid":"12baca79b6aec28ea6dc2d02e722eb0e5c80ea3c","tid":96232,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"橡膠子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b40c0690f580f6787e5465f79aae56fcdf54366","tid":96232,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:15:32.000Z","msg":"其實都幾反智<br />\n趕小販要出防暴隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b78a83185689f7e613185340b95c37dd0ccdea5","tid":96232,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"胡椒味魚蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a0aead4c89cb4279b77acfec7508ef242f7030","tid":96232,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:16:13.000Z","msg":"堅唔堅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a351492b74991f7d5434a8166e1e951f3f3ee0f","tid":96232,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"70e9d23f0db8329fc823e03b53fd11c7a3b3cea1","tid":96232,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,